1
00:00:00,330 --> 00:00:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lycanthrope?</font>

2
00:00:04,780 --> 00:00:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lycanthropes are those who 
carry the blood of Vargr,</font>

3
00:00:09,780 --> 00:00:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the wolf god of the ancient Vargr Kingdom.</font>

4
00:00:12,830 --> 00:00:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are a werewolf chosen by a god.</font>

5
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you know, werewolves have inherited 
that blood for generations,</font>

6
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the status and traditions 
that come with it.</font>

7
00:00:27,620 --> 00:00:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who wear that necklace,</font>

8
00:00:30,290 --> 00:00:33,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silver Fang, have the power
 to lead a pack.</font>

9
00:00:33,490 --> 00:00:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are great warriors. 
True Lycanthropes.</font>

10
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only old folks like me
 who know that now.</font>

11
00:00:47,750 --> 00:00:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you must feel that you're 
different from your kin somehow.</font>

12
00:00:55,260 --> 00:01:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone else naturally becomes a wolf 
under the light of the full moon,</i></font>

13
00:01:01,410 --> 00:01:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so why not me?</i></font>

14
00:01:04,730 --> 00:01:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I defective after all?</i></font>

15
00:01:09,330 --> 00:01:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're different from your kin 
because you were born to lead us.</font>

16
00:01:20,130 --> 00:01:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful. You're the one they're after.</font>

17
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan's capturing every 
werewolf he can</font>

18
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in order to acquire the blood 
of Vargr in your veins.</font>

19
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some of our kin have been 
hurt or even killed.</font>

20
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:42,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of me?</font>

21
00:01:45,810 --> 00:01:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

22
00:01:47,780 --> 00:01:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll pay for this!</font>

23
00:01:50,210 --> 00:01:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said the others 
were taken to Automnal.</font>

24
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

25
00:01:56,690 --> 00:01:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kamil and the others must be there—</font>

26
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear I'll save our brothers.</font>

27
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir, please tell us everything 
you can that might help us.</font>

28
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:42,990
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}<font size="30">- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</font></b></font>

29
00:03:45,010 --> 00:03:47,990
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="22">- Mortal Combat in Automnal -</font></b></font>

30
00:03:58,420 --> 00:04:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still haven't found one?!</font>

31
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. There wasn't one 
among the recently captured—</font>

32
00:04:04,510 --> 00:04:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep looking!</font>

33
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan!</font>

34
00:04:11,270 --> 00:04:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Release the princess this instant.</font>

35
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not too late.</font>

36
00:04:16,030 --> 00:04:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you're trying to do is unforgivable.</font>

37
00:04:21,990 --> 00:04:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this about status again?</font>

38
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. It's a matter of disposition.</font>

39
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That power wasn't passed down to 
those born into the royal family.</font>

40
00:04:31,090 --> 00:04:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was passed to those 
with the right disposition.</font>

41
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The royal family has 
merely protected that.</font>

42
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:39,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't worthy.</font>

43
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you were born a royal,</font>

44
00:04:42,730 --> 00:04:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a selfish man like you who sacrifices 
others could never acquire that power.</font>

45
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't be able to talk 
down to me for much longer.</font>

46
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's nothing you can do now.</font>

47
00:04:57,890 --> 00:05:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll prove that I was right,
 both back then and now.</font>

48
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:29,000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>What's wrong with this city?</i></font>

49
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>It's so lifeless.</i></font>

50
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:33,700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>All the residents are vampires.</i></font>

51
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:37,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>But no one's attacking us.</i></font>

52
00:05:39,450 --> 00:05:40,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Don't make eye contact.</i></font>

53
00:05:44,470 --> 00:05:48,800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>So the whole city is 
under Dardan's control?</i></font>

54
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>We're surrounded by enemies.</i></font>

55
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:55,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Right now, finding the sword comes first.</i></font>

56
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like the museum's under city hall.</font>

57
00:06:07,490 --> 00:06:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome to the Automnal Public Museum.</font>

58
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Trisha, the curator. This way.</font>

59
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Be careful, guys.</i></font>

60
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>She's no ordinary vampire.</i></font>

61
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In here. This is where the ancient
 furnishings are on display.</font>

62
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel free to look around.</font>

63
00:06:57,380 --> 00:06:58,640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>I found it!</i></font>

64
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Can we take it with us?</i></font>

65
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:07,490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>I'll try.</i></font>

66
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you came for that after all.</font>

67
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't be taking that sword.</font>

68
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you will die here.</font>

69
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli, take the sword 
while she's distracted!</font>

70
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? My hands 
are moving on their own!</font>

71
00:07:46,770 --> 00:07:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli!</font>

72
00:07:49,150 --> 00:07:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's happening?</font>

73
00:07:51,230 --> 00:07:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My hands...</font>

74
00:07:53,170 --> 00:07:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My body...</font>

75
00:07:55,930 --> 00:07:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't move!</font>

76
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sword may be fearsome, but what 
matters is which way it's pointing.</font>

77
00:08:08,340 --> 00:08:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I can control which way it points.</font>

78
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, you'll kill your friends with 
the blade you used to slaughter my kin!</font>

79
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I don't break free of her control, 
I'll cut down all of my friends.</font>

80
00:08:22,850 --> 00:08:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn. I can't move my own body!</i></font>

81
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is she controlling all 
seven of us by herself?</i></font>

82
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:32,900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Shion, can't you do anything?!</i></font>

83
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can hypnotize people, too!</font>

84
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion!</font>

85
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion!</font>

86
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

87
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noa...</font>

88
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wasting your time.</font>

89
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noa!</font>

90
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My body's moving on its own!</font>

91
00:09:20,450 --> 00:09:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noa!</font>

92
00:09:21,410 --> 00:09:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jaan!</font>

93
00:09:35,380 --> 00:09:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sol...</font>

94
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Solon!</font>

95
00:09:54,820 --> 00:09:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now everything will be mine.</i></font>

96
00:10:00,210 --> 00:10:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is just like back then.</font>

97
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Solon...</i></font>

98
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why is this happening?</i></font>

99
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noa!</font>

100
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn!</font>

101
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do?</font>

102
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love the looks on your faces.</font>

103
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could share this with someone.</font>

104
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I won't let 
you die that easily.</font>

105
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be a waste to end the fun so—</font>

106
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it! You'll pay for that!</font>

107
00:10:45,590 --> 00:10:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jino!</font>

108
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How does it feel to kill each other?</font>

109
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You poor thing.</font>

110
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was the perfect chance.</font>

111
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it!</i></font>

112
00:11:04,010 --> 00:11:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This ends now!</font>

113
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah...</font>

114
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only one left.</font>

115
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Off with his head!</font>

116
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jaan...</font>

117
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dare to defy me? How insolent!</font>

118
00:11:52,690 --> 00:11:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, you...</font>

119
00:12:08,050 --> 00:12:11,980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

120
00:12:12,060 --> 00:12:15,960
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

121
00:12:21,990 --> 00:12:23,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

122
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch. You just won't give up.</font>

123
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you!</font>

124
00:12:41,710 --> 00:12:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn. Too shallow.</i></font>

125
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:46,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've lost too much blood.</i></font>

126
00:12:46,310 --> 00:12:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm too slow.</i></font>

127
00:12:51,570 --> 00:12:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah!</font>

128
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wound is closing.</font>

129
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this Sooha's power?</font>

130
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the others...</i></font>

131
00:13:19,740 --> 00:13:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't good.</font>

132
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to finish this quickly.</font>

133
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That old man said the ship transporting 
our kind was going to Automnal, right?</font>

134
00:13:31,330 --> 00:13:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

135
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The harbor's over there.</font>

136
00:13:37,570 --> 00:13:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

137
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Tahel?</font>

138
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you find something?</font>

139
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's faint, but I smell 
our brothers over there.</font>

140
00:13:57,710 --> 00:13:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can move.</i></font>

141
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Taking damage has weakened 
her control considerably.</i></font>

142
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She can't control all seven 
of us at once after all.</i></font>

143
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She can only fully control one person.</i></font>

144
00:14:10,180 --> 00:14:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She can only stop the 
other six from moving.</i></font>

145
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now, she can't even fully control one.</i></font>

146
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which means she's running out of steam.</i></font>

147
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't move!</font>

148
00:14:30,410 --> 00:14:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now!</i></font>

149
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trena!</font>

150
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be...</font>

151
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's another one?</font>

152
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll pay for what you've done to Trisha.</font>

153
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure of that.</font>

154
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trisha stops your movements, 
and I cut off your heads.</font>

155
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, you can't beat us!</font>

156
00:15:11,020 --> 00:15:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jaan!</font>

157
00:15:14,190 --> 00:15:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah!</font>

158
00:15:17,590 --> 00:15:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion!</font>

159
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How?</font>

160
00:15:51,130 --> 00:15:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't bother!</font>

161
00:16:03,290 --> 00:16:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the last one.</font>

162
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take your head off 
with a single swing!</font>

163
00:16:13,930 --> 00:16:16,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

164
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha...</font>

165
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha?!</font>

166
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Trisha!</i></font>

167
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trisha...</font>

168
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

169
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bit me.</font>

170
00:16:57,040 --> 00:17:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you die...</font>

171
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

172
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is she? Did I imagine that?</font>

173
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was here a moment ago.</font>

174
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, I'd recognize her anywhere.</i></font>

175
00:17:20,950 --> 00:17:22,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Sooha, are you okay?!</i></font>

176
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:24,780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>To the woods.</i></font>

177
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:25,980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>The woods?</i></font>

178
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:29,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>When the full moon rises, 
the ritual will begin.</i></font>

179
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:33,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Before that happens, 
go to the Hivernal Woods.</i></font>

180
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:37,820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Before Dardan takes my power. Hurry!</i></font>

181
00:17:38,490 --> 00:17:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha.</font>

182
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was undoubtedly the 
princess's misty form ability.</font>

183
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She used it then, too.</font>

184
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness. Your Highness!</font>

185
00:18:22,890 --> 00:18:25,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Has her true power awoken?</i></font>

186
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she shouldn't have full use of it yet.</i></font>

187
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eventually, they'll all 
become mine anyway.</font>

188
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Dardan.</font>

189
00:18:39,250 --> 00:18:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

190
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've found a Lycanthrope.</font>

191
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha came here?</font>

192
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

193
00:18:50,210 --> 00:18:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She suddenly appeared and vanished?</font>

194
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that was her power.</font>

195
00:18:56,330 --> 00:18:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha told me</font>

196
00:18:58,710 --> 00:19:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she's currently trapped on the 
moon altar in the Hivernal Woods.</font>

197
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:05,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hivernal Woods?</font>

198
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

199
00:19:09,490 --> 00:19:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's here.</font>

200
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ritual will be held 
when the full moon rises.</font>

201
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to save Sooha before then, 
or Dardan will take her power.</font>

202
00:19:19,940 --> 00:19:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

203
00:19:20,850 --> 00:19:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The full moon? But that's tonight!</font>

204
00:19:24,770 --> 00:19:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you guys do it?</font>

205
00:19:29,370 --> 00:19:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who do you think you're talking to?</font>

206
00:19:32,890 --> 00:19:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course we can.</font>

207
00:19:36,410 --> 00:19:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of me, you—</font>

208
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we don't hurry, the moon's gonna rise.</font>

209
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

210
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Let's go.</font>

211
00:20:00,060 --> 00:20:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are corpses everywhere.</font>

212
00:20:01,890 --> 00:20:03,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened here?</font>

213
00:20:03,580 --> 00:20:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably because those sisters died.</font>

214
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These must be the low-ranking 
vampires they bit.</font>

215
00:20:11,630 --> 00:20:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It all started with Dardan, 
the First Vampire.</font>

216
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we defeat him, all the vampires 
he created will be destroyed.</font>

217
00:20:22,030 --> 00:20:24,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are our kin?</font>

218
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I was just asked to...</font>

219
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't breathe...</font>

220
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're holding the werewolves 
here somewhere, aren't you?</font>

221
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hand over the key.</font>

222
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:50,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kamil! Ruslan!</font>

223
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan! Guys!</font>

224
00:20:52,810 --> 00:20:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad!</font>

225
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:57,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mahan, you're okay.</font>

226
00:20:58,230 --> 00:20:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry we took so long.</font>

227
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you two hurt?</font>

228
00:21:02,810 --> 00:21:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're fine.</font>

229
00:21:04,990 --> 00:21:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had chances to escape, but we 
stayed to find out what's going on.</font>

230
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for making you worry.</font>

231
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. We're just glad you're okay.</font>

232
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are the others?</font>

233
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were taken somewhere else.</font>

234
00:21:21,830 --> 00:21:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

235
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To someplace called the moon altar.</font>

236
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moon altar?</font>

237
00:21:27,490 --> 00:21:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We heard it's in the woods nearby.</font>

238
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Let's go.</font>

239
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

240
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally found you, Lycanthrope.</font>

241
00:23:33,490 --> 00:23:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time, Episode 11: 
"Hazy Moon: Vargr's Blood."</i></font>

242
00:23:36,990 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="22">- Vargr's Blood -</font></b></font>

